{"tid":1307664,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"又話不受傷不被捕 原來都做唔到","createTime":"2019-07-11T16:12:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-11T16:53:48.000Z","uid":258696,"like":18,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"1dfcf0e65b44636076ae6ff05bfa73143e670d23","tid":1307664,"uid":258696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T16:12:26.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">又話不受傷不被捕<br />\n<br />\n而家係原來我地[size=6]<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">怕被捕 搞到日日有人受傷阿[</span></strong></span>/size=6]。<br />\n<br />\nCCTVB 紅媒由69開始都日日抹黑我地架啦，幾和平都抹黑架啦。<br />\n<br />\n唔好成日話人分散曬焦點，<br />\n<br />\n而家搞到我地變左下風既係因為士<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">氣唔夠</span></strong></span>，搞到大家無再成件事上曬腦咁再傾正經post。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n再吹捧黑帶打不還手啦。 實係會有一日有美軍黎救比人打既義士啦。<br />\n<br />\n屌我分化都係咁話。對面就日日派藍屍出黎，日日打人成班惡人<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">士氣高昂</span></strong>，大波man個柒頭就日日囂張咁樣。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">我地日日好似隻獵物，黑警藍屍就成個獵人咁，柒婆就日日諗d毒招分化我地，再係咁好快就收皮。</span>"},{"pid":"95e9f732e98950f9bb33ce6d6ec81129c74d7732","tid":1307664,"uid":258696,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T16:12:55.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">再講一百次<br />\n唔還手都擋<br />\n求下你地</span>"},{"pid":"854d344c6ad2e0b09c0539220472f74a0379a467","tid":1307664,"uid":258696,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T16:13:35.000Z","msg":"【任務欄】<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1306215\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1306215</a><br />\n任務眾多，請自行因應人數及背後目的考慮做邊D任 ；黃色為主線任務；紅色係Boss <br />\n7.11 - 梁烈士公眾告別禮 - <a href=\"http://t.me/leung711\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fleung711&d=mly3UyGsD7RWnvW57yDWjuSm5IdDYGcDmrHSDEWRKV4%3D&h=dc985f19\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/leung711</a><br />\n7.11 - 油尖旺區議會夢遊 - <a href=\"http://t.me/ytm_dc711\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fytm_dc711&d=mly3UyGsD7RWnvW57yDWjuSm5Id