core":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T16:27:47.000Z","msg":"好撚心痛 呢排做野忙 我都係咁推香港人7月時間表唔想大家out focus<br />\n<br />\n屌 點知由77開始 成日比人打 受傷<br />\n<br />\n612對住黑狗都無懼果份勇氣去左邊"},{"pid":"c56bf153b1d30358ee5e406ac9e5914f968a28bd","tid":1307664,"uid":258696,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T16:32:05.000Z","msg":"屌 又無人推"},{"pid":"23a4ca78862947762ecb610cd18c148c691184f9","tid":1307664,"uid":264369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"95e9f732e98950f9bb33ce6d6ec81129c74d7732","tid":1307664,"uid":258696,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T16:12:55.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">再講一百次<br />\n唔還手都擋<br />\n求下你地</span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T16:53:48.000Z","msg":"大埔斷手條片一開始就見兩個人開拖<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/groups/TaipoTaipo/permalink/10162150274315245?sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fgroups%2FTaipoTaipo%2Fpermalink%2F10162150274315245%3Fsfns%3Dmo&d=mly3UyGsD7RWnvW57yDWjuSm5IdDYGcDmrHSDEWRKV4%3D&h=a59419ca\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/groups/TaipoTaipo/permalink/10162150274315245?sfns=mo</a><br />\n另一隻藍屍狗即時幫拖從後襲擊，之後有人分隔開佢地，前後不足１０秒．<br />\n<br />\n手足受傷，人人都唔想，希望佢快Ｄ好番．<br />\n另外，先問下佢本人打唔打算追究，因為片中佢都有出手．決定追究的話，大家就要幫手搵番個兩條扑街出黎．<br />\n片中所見，傷者似係護牆心切企錯位，背靠人群企的話事情結果應該會唔同．<br />\n一直都話 be water．尤其對家擺明挑機，更應小心．"}]}